-- Bilfinger Berger Reaches Financial Close for Hospital Project in Toronto
-- Mike Gavin
-- 2010-07-15T09:07:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-15/bilfinger-berger-reaches-financial-close-for-hospital-project-in-toronto.html

          
          
             Bilfinger Berger AG reached
financial close on a public-private partnership project in
Ontario’s health system, the company said in an e-mailed
statement today.  
 The project, with an investment volume of about 340 million
euros, includes the planning, financing, construction and
operation of the new Women’s College Hospital in Toronto.
Bilfinger Berger is investing own capital of 27 million euros,
it said.  
          
          


  


        